MF9AUD.original: ~z~If you don't want to make things real difficult for him you're going to come to Comrades Bar on Mohawk. I have a work for you.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~你要是不想让他难做，就到Mohawk的Comrades酒吧来。我有活给你。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~You been a useful set of hands. Look after yourself.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~你一直都是个好帮手。照顾好自己。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Who'd a thought an immigrant from the wrong side of the Adriatic would be the most reliable soldier we got?
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Who'd a thought an immigrant from the wrong side of the Adriatic would be the most reliable soldier we got?

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Niko, what's up, listen. This family's falling a-fucking part.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Niko, what's up, listen. This family's falling a-fucking part.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Hey, yokel. What the fuck? That car you got to me, it looked like shit. I got a hot date tonight.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~喂，乡巴佬。你搞毛？你给我弄来的车，烂得跟坨屎一样。今晚我还有个火热的约会呢。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Who knows what's happened to him. Think of all the money you coulda made.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Who knows what's happened to him. Think of all the money you coulda made.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~What'd'ya mean, Niko? We're family. We've welcomed you into the fold.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~What'd'ya mean, Niko? We're family. We've welcomed you into the fold.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Don't worry about that cousin of yours, he won't be in no danger sleeping in your Algonquin pad by his self.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Don't worry about that cousin of yours, he won't be in no danger sleeping in your Algonquin pad by his self.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Hey, sorry things didn't work out, goodbye.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Hey, sorry things didn't work out, goodbye.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Too bad, man. It was clean, wasn't it? Well, maybe you should stay home. Goodbye.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~太糟了，老弟。车本来是干净的吧？大概你还是该待在家里。再见。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I guess I will. The horse is gone and I can't get Phil on the phone.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I guess I will. The horse is gone and I can't get Phil on the phone.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Hey baby, how about I take your beautiful ass out tonight? Maybe we can take one of your fat boyfriend's cabs...
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Hey baby, how about I take your beautiful ass out tonight? Maybe we can take one of your fat boyfriend's cabs...

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I'm not in the family, I'm your employee, Mr. Pegorino. You seem to get this stuff confused.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I'm not in the family, I'm your employee, Mr. Pegorino. You seem to get this stuff confused.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~We're back on top, Niko. The Pegorinos is still somebody.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~我们重振雄风了，Niko。Pegorino家族还是有地位的。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~She won't be impressed with the way you look, so clean car is good thing. Later on.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~她不会对你的长相留下好印象的，所以一辆干净的车也还不错。回见。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Don't get cute, kid. It don't suit you. You're staying in Alderney now, just like me and Phil.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Don't get cute, kid. It don't suit you. You're staying in Alderney now, just like me and Phil.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~A nice apartment in Alderney City, on Mahesh Avenue. Real classy.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~A nice apartment in Alderney City, on Mahesh Avenue. Real classy.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I bought some of his debt for him. Now he don't have to worry about no loansharks coming after him, just me.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I bought some of his debt for him. Now he don't have to worry about no loansharks coming after him, just me.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Money's not what motivates everyone, Mr. Pegorino. I had more important things to think about.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Money's not what motivates everyone, Mr. Pegorino. I had more important things to think about.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~This is a gift, Jimmy, or a way for you to keep your eye on me?
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~This is a gift, Jimmy, or a way for you to keep your eye on me?

MF9AUD.original: ~z~And that means we're looking after your cousin too. That guy likes to gamble, don't he?
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~And that means we're looking after your cousin too. That guy likes to gamble, don't he?

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I'm my own man and I follow my own instincts.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I'm my own man and I follow my own instincts.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I never made any promises to you, Mr. Pegorino.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I never made any promises to you, Mr. Pegorino.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I'd prefer to be a paid employee than a relative.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I'd prefer to be a paid employee than a relative.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Forget about it. I'm gonna hold onto it for a while. Least I could do. Ciao.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Forget about it. I'm gonna hold onto it for a while. Least I could do. Ciao.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~That's something you're going to have to accept.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~That's something you're going to have to accept.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Ha, sure, Niko. I'm giving you a gift.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Ha, sure, Niko. I'm giving you a gift.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~You don't need to do that for my cousin, Mr. Pegorino. I can handle all his debt. I'll cover it.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~You don't need to do that for my cousin, Mr. Pegorino. I can handle all his debt. I'll cover it.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Now, I'm out. I don't want to get involved in this shit no more. Good luck to you.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Now, I'm out. I don't want to get involved in this shit no more. Good luck to you.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Hello, this is Vladimir's answer phone message. Be leaving a recording for me after the buzz has been playing.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~你好，这里是Vladimir的留言信箱。请在蜂鸣声后向我留言。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Dimitri and I had unfinished business so I went ahead and finished it.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Dimitri and I had unfinished business so I went ahead and finished it.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Niko, It's Jimmy. You're doing real well, kid. You're becoming part of the family.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Niko, It's Jimmy. You're doing real well, kid. You're becoming part of the family.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~You better start remembering important people you dumb peasant. Your cousin owes me a lot of money.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~你最好记住那些大人物，蠢蛋土包子。你堂兄可欠了我一大笔钱。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Niko, the shit has gone down. I need to see you. Come to the club in Tudor.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，情况不太妙，我需要见你。到Tudor的俱乐部来。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~For a peasant you did okay. Car looks good. Girl I'm taking out tonight is going to be impressed.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~作为一个乡巴佬你的表现还不错。车子看上去很好。今晚我带出去的姑娘会有个好印象的。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Hey, let's keep this a business relationship.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Hey, let's keep this a business relationship.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Alright Mr. Pegorino, I'll see you there.
~z~How hard would it have been to suck up your pride to do one deal? Now, I got nothing left to lose.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~How hard would it have been to suck up your pride to do one deal? Now, I got nothing left to lose.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Vlad? Name doesn't ring any bells. I'm sorry.
~z~You're a snake. You've turned around and bit the hand that fed you.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~You're a snake. You've turned around and bit the hand that fed you.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Salve. This is Jimmy Pegorino's phone. Leave a message.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~你好，这是Jimmy Pegorino的电话。请留言。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I had that deal set up. I needed this, it was my only way back in and you fucked me.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~I had that deal set up. I needed this, it was my only way back in and you fucked me.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Phil's bringing me my taste of the cash and Dimitri's still got hold of the horse. This is perfect.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Phil会把分成给我，Dimitri手上的海马也还在。太完美了。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~You smug fucking bastard, after all I done for you, you play me like this.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~You smug fucking bastard, after all I done for you, you play me like this.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~Ahh, the dumb yokel, I meant to call this girl I'm seeing.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~Ahh, the dumb yokel, I meant to call this girl I'm seeing.

MF9AUD.original: ~z~I hope your partnership is a fruitful one. Good luck and goodbye.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~希望你们的合作能有好结果。祝你好运，再见。

MF9AUD.original: ~z~We're lucky to have you in the family.
MF9AUD.translated: ~z~We're lucky to have you in the family.
